node.text:
Hiiii friends 💙 I’ve teamed up with Shattered Glass Artist @theunsigned.artist and @Canvas.for.causes to Raffle off this 1/1 Signed Neo-Mosaic Glass art piece! 
The Proceed from this raffle will be donated to one of my favorite organizations to support, “Farm stead of New England, Farmsteads of New England is a unique program that works to empower adults with autism by providing meaningful lives.
Your donations help to provide a high quality of life to those that this program supports and to expand for others who are in need of these services! (#farmsteadsofnewengland) 
The Link to enter is in my bio.
Winner will be chosen via Lottery Wheel Monday 9/20/21
And posted on my story.
•
Raffle Tickets are only $10 each and we also have a second option to purchased a signed canvas print. See link in bio for details.
•
RAFFLE STARTS NOW!! GOOD LUCK!! Thank you all in advance for your generous donations 💙🙏🏾 and make sure to follow @TheUnsigned.Artist & @Canvas.for.causes for updates on the raffle!
•
#theunsignedartist #canvasforcauses
#donate #MercedesVarnando #Raffle #farmsteadsofnewengland
